title: Elite Gourmet ETO236 Personal Compact 2 Slice Countertop Toaster Oven with 15 Minute Timer & Adjustable Temperature, Bake, Broil, & Toast, Black
description: Stay toasty with the Elite Gourmet 2 slice toaster oven. Toast bagels and bread, bake a personal pizza, or broil an open-faced sandwich. With an adjustable timer and heat selector functions, cooking is fast and easy. With its compact design, cleanup and storage is simple and hassle-free. The attractive Black finish makes this toaster oven The perfect addition to any kitchen.
